ecords|DECCA]]  DK 11 560/1-2\n*Mozart, ''[[The Magic Flute|Die Zauberfl\u00f6te]]'', K. 620 ([[Lucia Popp|Popp]], Krauss, [[Werner Krenn|Krenn]]), Vienna Haydn Orchestra (1967), [[Decca Records|DECCA]] DK 11 560/1-2\n*Mozart, ''[[La clemenza di Tito]]'', K. 621 ([[Teresa Berganza|Berganza]], Casula, [[Brigitte Fassbaender|Fassbaender]], [[Lucia Popp|Popp]], Krenn, Franc), [[Vienna State Opera|Vienna State Opera Orchestra and Choir]] (1967), [[Decca Records|DECCA]] SET 357/59\n*Mozart, \"Masonic Funeral Music\", (Fischer, Krenn, Krause), London Symphony Orchestra (1968), [[Decca Records|DECCA]] SXL 6409\n*Mozart:\n**Piano Concerto No. 8 in C major, K. 246\n**[[Piano Concerto No. 9 (Mozart)|Piano Concerto No. 9]] in E-flat major, \"Jeunehomme\", K. 271\n**Rondo in A minor, K. 511 ([[Vladimir Ashkenazy|Ashkenazy]]), London Symphony Orchestra (1966), [[Decca Records|DECCA]] SXL 6259\n*Mozart\n**[[Piano Concerto No. 17 (Mozart)|Piano Concerto No. 17]] in G major, K. 453\n**[[Piano Concerto No. 26 (Mozart)|Piano Concerto No. 26]] in D major, \"Coronation\", K. 537 (Richter-Haaser), [[Philharmonia|London Philharmonia Orchestra]], [[EMI]] 1 047 - 50506\n*Mozart\n**[[Piano Concerto No. 23 (Mozart)|Piano Concerto No. 23]] in A major, K. 488\n**[[Piano Concerto No. 24 (Mozart)|Piano Concerto No. 24]] in C minor, K. 491 ([[Clifford Curzon|Curzon]]), London Symphony Orchestra (1967, [[Decca Records|DECCA]]  SXL 6354\n*Mozart, [[Piano Concerto No. 27 (Mozart)|Piano Concerto No. 27]] in B flat major, K.595 ([[Clifford Curzon|Curzon]]), London Symphony Orchestra (1967), [[Philips Records|Philips-DECCA]] 456757\n*Mozart, ''\"Mozart Festival\"'', Vol. I, Vienna Haydn Orchestra, [[Decca Records|DECCA]] DK 11 536/1-2\n*Mozart, ''\"Mozart Festival\"'', Vol. II, Vienna Philharmonic Orchestra, [[Decca Records|DECCA]] DK 11 560/1-2\n*Mozart, [[Requiem (Mozart)|Requiem]] in D minor, K. 626 ([[Elly Ameling|Ameling]], [[Marilyn Horne|Horne]], Benelli, Franc), Vienna Philharmonic Orchestra (1